<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<style>
  header {
    background-image: url("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1494177310973-4841f7d5a882?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=2342&q=80");
    background-size: cover;
  }
  footer {
    background-color: #0A2647:
  }
  .pic {
    object-fit: cover;
  }
</style>

<body>
  <!-- Header -->
  <header class="text-white py-5">
    <div class="container text-center" style="padding: 250px; position:relative;">
      <div class="container text-center" style="position: absolute; top: 60px; left: 0">
        <h1 class="text-center" style="font-size: 70px">Connect with athletes <br> in your area...</h1>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>



<div class="container mb-5" style="padding: 20px; column-gap: 20px">
    <div style="padding: 20px">
      <h1>Featured Events:</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="row" style="">
      <div class="col-md-8">
        <div id="carouselExampleIndicators" class="carousel slide">
          <div class="carousel-indicators">
            <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide-to="0" class="active" aria-current="true" aria-label="Slide 1"></button>
            <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide-to="1" aria-label="Slide 2"></button>
            <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide-to="2" aria-label="Slide 3"></button>
          </div>
          <div class="carousel-inner">
            <% @groups.each do |group| %>
            <%= link_to group_path(group) do%>
            <div class="carousel-item active">
              <%= cl_image_tag group.photo.key, class: 'd-block w-100 rounded pic', height: '450', width: '350'%>
            </div>
            <%end%>
            <%end%>
          </div>
          <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide="prev">
            <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
          </button>
          <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide="next">
            <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <h1>About us</h1>
        <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Delectus quas tempore expedita iste voluptatem quisquam reprehenderit odit impedit aliquid, natus consectetur odio, nam quo voluptatum excepturi illum, explicabo eveniet atque.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</html>
